---
title: Monterey Jack Burger with Red Onion Marmalade and Crispy Zucchini Fries
description: This, my friends, is the burger that tops ALL burgers. And we’ve got Monterey Jack (and our chefs, Freida and Nate, of course) to thank for that. We balance out this hearty dish by swapping out traditional fries for lighter zucchini ones.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-and-beef-burgers-d505f937.jpg
